      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRINCE BERNARDO (7) scored two back then drifted back and missed the frame latest finishing a 8 length 6th at this track (20.24). Comes through a solid form race last start. Ready to return to form. SALAMAT (8) is racing well without winning, recording seven minors on end, the latest hitting the ground running with a fast early sectional but finishing in the minors again when second (19.79) over 340m at this track. Yet to miss the placings from four starts out of this box. Will give a great sight again. VISTA YTTRIUM (1) settled down midfield and held his position to the line when finishing 4th (20.01) at this track. Cannot be underestimated. TIPSY ETHICS (2) found the frame for the second consecutive time when narrowly beaten into third last time out (20.18) over 340m at this track.",
